      "recording_id": "aa907076-d7e7-4bfe-9bc3-f35cb231b754",
      "end_time": 29.61,
      "start_time": 20.66,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8f714552-79cf-4713-a10a-d03d6a298bcc",
      "order_number": 4,
      "text": "Mm Thank you for calling. This is Ashley, how may I help you?"
    },
    {
      "id": "d1751998-7289-49d4-94ad-6968414d1709",
      "recording_id": "aa907076-d7e7-4bfe-9bc3-f35cb231b754",
      "end_time": 33.66,
      "start_time": 30.09,
      "recording_attendee_id": "912f0049-e21c-4aff-888d-9ba13fc2316e",
      "order_number": 5,
      "text": "Hey Ashley, good afternoon. It's Brandon calling with rentable, how are you?"
    },
    {
      "id": "d1751998-7289-49d4-94ad-6968414d1709",
      "recording_id": "aa907076-d7e7-4bfe-9bc3-f35cb231b754",
      "end_time": 34.54,
      "start_time": 33.69,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8f714552-79cf-4713-a10a-d03d6a298bcc",
      "order_number": 6,
      "text": "Good, how are you?"
    },
    {
      "id": "d1751998-7289-49d4-94ad-6968414d1709",
      "recording_id": "aa907076-d7e7-4bfe-9bc3-f35cb231b754",
      "end_time": 64.15,
      "start_time": 34.86,
      "recording_attendee_id": "912f0049-e21c-4aff-888d-9ba13fc2316e",
      "order_number": 7,
      "text": "I'm good, I'm good. Hey I just actually got off a call with with my colleague Russell. Um and he had mentioned that he had met with you a while back, he used to work in the Carolinas now transitioned down into Tampa florida, but I recently took over and I was hoping um I know you guys obviously talked back then but um I was hoping to maybe schedule some time on the calendar to learn a little bit more about how you guys are doing with your marketing and occupancy and and see if now might be a better time to um revisit rentable."
    },
    {
      "id": "d1751998-7289-49d4-94ad-6968414d1709",
      "recording_id": "aa907076-d7e7-4bfe-9bc3-f35cb231b754",
      "end_time": 69.64,
      "start_time": 64.7,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8f714552-79cf-4713-a10a-d03d6a298bcc",
      "order_number": 8,
      "text": "Okay. Um Would you can I give you my email and have you email me and I can get back to you on the time?"
    },
    {
      "id": "d1751998-7289-49d4-94ad-6968414d1709",
      "recording_id": "aa907076-d7e7-4bfe-9bc3-f35cb231b754",
      "end_time": 73.42,
      "start_time": 70.82,
      "recording_attendee_id": "912f0049-e21c-4aff-888d-9ba13fc2316e",
      "order_number": 9,
      "text": "Yeah, absolutely, I can definitely do that. Um"
    },
    {
      "id": "d1751998-7289-49d4-94ad-6968414d1709",
      "recording_id": "aa907076-d7e7-4bfe-9bc3-f35cb231b754",
      "end_time": 75.43,
      "start_time": 74.88,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8f714552-79cf-4713-a10a-d03d6a298bcc",
      "order_number": 10,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "id": "d1751998-7289-49d4-94ad-6968414d1709",
      "recording_id": "aa907076-d7e7-4bfe-9bc3-f35cb231b754",
      "end_time": 86.76,
      "start_time": 75.04,
      "recording_attendee_id": "912f0049-e21c-4aff-888d-9ba13fc2316e",
      "order_number": 11,
      "text": "I know I know I personally this week have to have some time um most days in the morning and then sparingly in the afternoon, so that gives you a better idea right now on the phone, I could always book it, but do you want me"
    },
    {
      "id": "d1751998-7289-49d4-94ad-6968414d1709",
      "recording_id": "aa907076-d7e7-4bfe-9bc3-f35cb231b754",
      "end_time": 88.65,
      "start_time": 86.76,
      "recording_attendee_id": "912f0049-e21c-4aff-888d-9ba13fc2316e",
      "order_number": 12,
      "text": "to email you that that works as well?"
    },
    {
      "id": "d1751998-7289-49d4-94ad-6968414d1709",
      "recording_id": "aa907076-d7e7-4bfe-9bc3-f35cb231b754",
      "end_time": 98.44,
      "start_time": 88.68,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8f714552-79cf-4713-a10a-d03d6a298bcc",
      "order_number": 13,
      "text": "Uh well I can tell you I'm sorry. We, so we've had some transitions um in our company and so I've taken on a lot more responsibility. And"
    },
    {
      "id": "d1751998-7289-49d4-94ad-6968414d1709",
      "recording_id": "aa907076-d7e7-4bfe-9bc3-f35cb231b754",
      "end_time": 98.96,
      "start_time": 98.42,
      "recording_attendee_id": "912f0049-e21c-4aff-888d-9ba13fc2316e",
      "order_number": 14,
      "text": "Right,"
    },
    {
      "id": "d1751998-7289-49d4-94ad-6968414d1709",
      "recording_id": "aa907076-d7e7-4bfe-9bc3-f35cb231b754",
      "end_time": 109.9,
      "start_time": 98.44,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8f714552-79cf-4713-a10a-d03d6a298bcc",
      "order_number": 15,
      "text": "so with that I'm having, I'm like in a ton of meetings. So right now uh the earliest I have would be of September twenty-two I don't know if that would work for you is a Wednesday."
