    {
      "id": "d1751998-7289-49d4-94ad-6968414d1709",
      "recording_id": "aa907076-d7e7-4bfe-9bc3-f35cb231b754",
      "end_time": 123.61,
      "start_time": 110.07,
      "recording_attendee_id": "912f0049-e21c-4aff-888d-9ba13fc2316e",
      "order_number": 16,
      "text": "okay, okay. Yeah, I can definitely put it on the calendar for sure. Um what does I guess in in just in regards to that when you guys typically go through your budgeting and and things of that nature for IOS and things."
    },
    {
      "id": "d1751998-7289-49d4-94ad-6968414d1709",
      "recording_id": "aa907076-d7e7-4bfe-9bc3-f35cb231b754",
      "end_time": 132.23,
      "start_time": 124.36,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8f714552-79cf-4713-a10a-d03d6a298bcc",
      "order_number": 17,
      "text": "Um We get that finalized by the end of the year. I typically look at it. Um and get all my portions finalized in november."
    },
    {
      "id": "d1751998-7289-49d4-94ad-6968414d1709",
      "recording_id": "aa907076-d7e7-4bfe-9bc3-f35cb231b754",
      "end_time": 149.69,
      "start_time": 132.67,
      "recording_attendee_id": "912f0049-e21c-4aff-888d-9ba13fc2316e",
      "order_number": 18,
      "text": "Okay, so September, middle of September might be a a good time to to meet, I can definitely let's throw some time on the calendar and we can revisit it, if if you find a quick fifteen minutes, it won't take too long. But if you find a quick fifteen minutes before that we can always reschedule and move it up. Um"
    },
    {
      "id": "d1751998-7289-49d4-94ad-6968414d1709",
      "recording_id": "aa907076-d7e7-4bfe-9bc3-f35cb231b754",
      "end_time": 155.92,
      "start_time": 149.23,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8f714552-79cf-4713-a10a-d03d6a298bcc",
      "order_number": 19,
      "text": "Okay. Oh if it only takes about fifteen minutes. Um let's see. I could do September one."
    },
    {
      "id": "d1751998-7289-49d4-94ad-6968414d1709",
      "recording_id": "aa907076-d7e7-4bfe-9bc3-f35cb231b754",
      "end_time": 162.75,
      "start_time": 156.13,
      "recording_attendee_id": "912f0049-e21c-4aff-888d-9ba13fc2316e",
      "order_number": 20,
      "text": "Okay for sure. Let's uh what time September one works best for you?"
